Class VisualDistractorParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • parameters.Parameter
      • parameters.VisualDistractorParameter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class VisualDistractorParameter
extends Parameter
    This is a children class of Parameter. It encapsulate the behaviour of the visual distractor during the experiment The visual distractor displays numerous geometric shapes one at time.
